3.  Attributes and Variables                                 Command Referenceroute.auto_via_ladder.generate_center_track_on_off_grid_pattern_must_join_pin_shapes

NAME
       route.auto_via_ladder.generate_center_track_on_off_grid_pat-
       tern_must_join_pin_shapes
              Specifies  whether  via  ladder  commands should auto-generate a
              default track on any pattern_must_join shape found  to  be  off-
              track.

TYPE
       Boolean

DEFAULT
       false

DESCRIPTION
       Specifies  whether  via  ladder commands should auto-generate a default
       track on any pattern_must_join shape found to be off-track.  If  appro-
       priate,  a track will be generated through the center of the pin shape,
       running in the preferred direction of the pin layer.

       The generated track is visible only during via ladder commands and can-
       not be used by regular routing commands.

       The default is false.

